“Well, then,” interrupted Bunger, “give him your left arm for bait to get 
the right. Do you know, gentlemen”—very gravely and mathematically bowing 
to each Captain in succession—“Do you know, gentlemen, that the digestive 
organs of the whale are so inscrutably constructed by Divine Providence, that 
